    <string name="explain_interval_connection_mob_text">Interval connection turns off %1$s when the device sleeps and only re-connects every %2$s min for %3$s min (interval and duration can be changed in settings) to fetch new messages. Depending on the \'Switch-on when unlocking\' setting it is also turned on when the device is unlocked.</string>
